s Snapshot\n\nhubspot — `search` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Fetch Changes Since Watermark · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"a8a6e096-09bf-bab9-cc71-98d5eba400f6","name":"Note: Load Previous Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fetch Changes Since Watermark\n\nGET https://api.example.com/v1/contacts — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Normalize Records · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"4e5c1c5a-caf2-778e-3465-af6fdb3e1525","name":"Note: Fetch Changes Since Watermark"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Normalize Records\n\nCustom JavaScript: Normalize incoming contact records to a stable schema\n\nNext: Fingerprint for Idempotency","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"b5a84bcf-f695-c5df-0900-684c0bc2d502","name":"Note: Normalize Records"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fingerprint for Idempotency\n\nCustom JavaScript: Build a stable idempotency key per contact (djb2 hash, no deps)\n\nNext: Drop Already-Processed Items","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,520],"id":"4376bc80-a57f-b440-84c7-872683d19f2f","name":"Note: Fingerprint for Idempotency"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Drop Already-Processed Items\n\nCross-execution dedupe: remembers keys it has processed before and drops repeats — the idempotency guard.\n\nNext: Upsert into Google Sheets","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,520],"id":"9eea9d3b-ee89-e49f-8621-01a0f68db79a","name":"Note: Drop Already-Processed Items"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Upsert into Google Sheets\n\ngoogleSheets — `appendOrUpdate` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Advance Watermark · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1614,520],"id":"34a5084e-a3a2-6bc3-574f-49e14cee8e92","name":"Note: Upsert into Google Sheets"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Advance Watermark\n\nCustom JavaScript: Advance the incremental watermark to the newest record seen\n\nNext: Persist Watermark (HubSpot)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,520],"id":"c97ad32d-e644-aaa0-156e-6030a2560d3c","name":"Note: Advance Watermark"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Watermark (HubSpot)\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Row Counts Match? · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,520],"id":"c3c21638-3496-e339-35f6-3407fb57ce38","name":"Note: Persist Watermark (HubSpot)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Row Counts Match?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.processed >= 0 }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Load Previous Snapshot 2 · ②→ Raise Drift Alarm","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2586,520],"id":"cc1a2102-99a6-a5f9-b8af-ed659c7dd614","name":"Note: Row Counts Match?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Raise Drift Alarm\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,970],"id":"d749405a-307f-cd7a-e3b2-ceb0aeed48f4","name":"Note: Raise Drift Alarm"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Load Previous Snapshot 2\n\nnotion — `getAll` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Compute Drift vs Snapshot · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"472fc1d0-06aa-4f12-178c-a65ba013c33c","name":"Note: Load Previous Snapshot 2"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Compute Drift vs Snapshot\n\nCustom JavaScript: Compare current metrics with the previous snapshot\n\nNext: Stamp Completion Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"7b0852cc-aa21-7519-c796-f5149f92193e","name":"Note: Compute Drift vs Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Completion Time\n\nStamps `completedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Persist Run Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,520],"id":"5b84ebb9-4d67-fb68-2e4a-4a4880d71e1c","name":"Note: Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Run Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Enrich with Reference Data","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4206,520],"id":"cb81ea6e-2e65-f85f-33bf-9ea19e57abbf","name":"Note: Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Enrich with Reference Data\n\nGET https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Fold In Enrichment Fields · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4530,520],"id":"97e4489b-e7a3-a520-cfcd-39c63b923f2c","name":"Note: Enrich with Reference Data"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fold In Enrichment Fields\n\nShapes the item: writes `enrichedAt`, `enrichmentSource`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Serialize Run Output (CSV)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,520],"id":"f5740fa8-2595-5ffd-ff08-5d0f066aa38b","name":"Note: Fold In Enrichment Fields"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Serialize Run Output (CSV)\n\nSerializes items to a CSV binary file.\n\nNext: Archive Copy to Google Drive","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,520],"id":"7707b70e-7207-ea44-1212-2af0c80f4408","name":"Note: Serialize Run Output (CSV)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Copy to Google Drive\n\ngoogleDrive — `upload` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,520],"id":"51fe3e85-07bd-022d-82ab-fe79aef842dc","name":"Note: Archive Copy to Google Drive"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow\n\nDelegates to a reusable sub-workflow (single-responsibility building block) and waits for its result.\n\nPorts: ①→ Record Sub-workflow Result · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,520],"id":"4d08da9e-09f2-79c3-ef32-f44e7980d195","name":"Note: Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Record Sub-workflow Result\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Save Execution Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6150,520],"id":"9b5eb4d5-e339-52ce-a281-30951c235067","name":"Note: Record Sub-workflow Result"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Save Execution Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Stamp Processing Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6474,520],"id":"b83f7f36-046c-4102-7956-4eeba7748738","name":"Note: Save Execution Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Processing Time\n\nStamps `processedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Guard Non-Empty email","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6798,520],"id":"54029fb1-e922-aea5-330b-d77cd0b686f0","name":"Note: Stamp Processing Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Guard Non-Empty email\n\nDrops items that fail the condition; only qualifying items continue (no false branch).\n\nNext: Align Field Names","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7122,520],"id":"8134a73f-652f-c72b-5321-2d81b4a0afa5","name":"Note: Guard Non-Empty email"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Align Field Names\n\nNormalizes field names so every source feeds the same downstream schema.\n\nNext: Sort Contacts Newest First","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7446,520],"id":"78ba063b-7de1-c4cf-2dc0-6344ce789202","name":"Note: Align Field Names"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Sort Contacts Newest First\n\nOrders items (newest first) so limits and digests pick the most relevant records.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7770,520],"id":"fb86b8fb-4d3c-453f-6ab2-88f708f6e30a","name":"Note: Sort Contacts Newest First"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Notion)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8094,520],"id":"17c942a4-8cae-c321-01d5-aff536178794","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Notion)\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Telegram · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8418,520],"id":"3d7f2958-82fc-d1b6-2f84-e92fe352a721","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Notion)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Telegram\n\ntelegram — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Telegram bot token","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8742,520],"id":"bafe1b06-fca2-4e0b-4973-dc5fcbed23c1","name":"Note: Send Summary to Telegram"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8094,1540],"id":"7e960945-c767-ef64-348e-60514dc2b152","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8418,1540],"id":"f90c3d00-79cf-9bc2-16e6-b01df2b6b931","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8742,1540],"id":"4b782e3f-b541-aaf1-6e0f-4f8aba30a119","name":"Note: Park in Dead-Letter Queue"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Mirror contacts across systems with HubSpot and Google Drive without manual work\n\n**Pattern:** Two-System Sync · **Level:** Architect · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nMirror contacts across systems with HubSpot and Google Drive without manual work. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual follow-ups is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nWeekly Schedule → Load Previous Snapshot → Fetch Changes Since Watermark → Normalize Records → Fingerprint for Idempotency → Drop Already-Processed Items → Upsert into Google Sheets → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to two-system sync without manual effort\n- Anyone automating follow-ups in sales\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n- Keeps your systems in sync\n- Removes copy-paste errors\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; Google OAuth2; Google OAuth2 / service account; HubSpot private-app token; Notion integration token; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"c0acc749-5933-e44b-15d7-43bfc0f11805","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Failures are also parked in a dead-letter queue for replay. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-20],"id":"dce45fa5-94c5-f999-3f4c-355143e8880d","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🧹 Data quality\n\nDedupe/diff steps make re-runs safe: the same input twice will not create duplicate records. If you change the key fields, clear n8n's dedupe memory (node → 'Clear stored keys') before the next run.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-20],"id":"7736faca-d003-0f69-eb47-bf458e238e80","name":"🧹 Data quality"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your follow-ups process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-20],"id":"a14dbdbb-3679-84d3-f15f-8338bf4ed22e","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Weekly Schedule":{"main":[[{"node":"Load Previous Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Load Previous Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Fetch Changes Since Watermark","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fetch Changes Since Watermark":{"main":[[{"node":"Normalize Records","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Normalize Records":{"main":[[{"node":"Fingerprint for Idempotency","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fingerprint for Idempotency":{"main":[[{"node":"Drop Already-Processed Items","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Drop Already-Processed Items":{"main":[[{"node":"Upsert into Google Sheets","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Upsert into Google Sheets":{"main":[[{"node":"Advance Watermark","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Advance Watermark":{"main":[[{"node":"Persist Watermark (HubSpot)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Persist Watermark (HubSpot)":{"main":[[{"node":"Row Counts Match?","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Row Counts Match?":{"main":[[{"node":"Load Previous Snapshot 2","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Raise Drift Alarm","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Load Previous Snapshot 2":{"main":[[{"node":"Compute Drift vs Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Compute Drift vs Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Completion Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Completion Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Persist Run Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Persist Run Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Enrich with Reference Data","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Enrich with Reference Data":{"main":[[{"node":"Fold In Enrichment Fields","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fold In Enrichment Fields":{"main":[[{"node":"Serialize Run Output (CSV)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Serialize Run Output (CSV)":{"main":[[{"node":"Archive Copy to Google Drive","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Archive Copy to Google Drive":{"main":[[{"node":"Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow":{"main":[[{"node":"Record Sub-workflow Result","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Record Sub-workflow Result":{"main":[[{"node":"Save Execution Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Save Execution Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Processing Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Processing Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Guard Non-Empty email","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Guard Non-Empty email":{"main":[[{"node":"Align Field Names","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Align Field Names":{"main":[[{"node":"Sort Contacts Newest First","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Sort Contacts Newest First":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Notion)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Notion)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Telegram","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Escalate Failure to Slack":{"main":[[{"node":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Raise Drift Alarm":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Telegram":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"74039af4-6135-4f08-bb61-b171f2e5868f","id":"FDX08221"}